'''乔纳森·克里斯蒂安·戴维'''（{{lang-en|Jonathan Christian David}}；{{bd|2000年|1月14日}}），是一名加拿大足球运动员，场上司职[[前锋_(足球)|前锋]]，目前效力于[[法国足球甲级联赛|法甲]]球队[[里尔足球俱乐部|里尔]]，并代表[[加拿大国家男子足球队|加拿大国家男子足球队]]参加国际比赛。

==青年队生涯==
戴维在10岁时开始为[[渥太华|渥太华]]球队格洛斯特龙之队出战正规比赛。<ref name="CSA">{{Cite web |title=Jonathan David |url=https://www.canadasoccer.com/profile/?id=6522 |access-date=2019-05-11 |publisher=加拿大足球 |archive-date=2021-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210602234809/https://canadasoccer.com/profile/?id=6522 }}</ref>一年后，他加入了渥太华格洛斯特，并为球队的黄蜂队效力至2015年。<ref name="CSA" /><ref name="RCI">{{Cite web |last=Kilkenny |first=Carmel |date=2018-09-11 |title=Jonathan David impresses on the national team |url=http://www.rcinet.ca/en/2018/09/11/jonathan-david-impresses-on-the-national-team/ |access-date=2019-05-11 |publisher=Radio Canada International |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204221021/https://www.rcinet.ca/en/2018/09/11/jonathan-david-impresses-on-the-national-team/ }}</ref>2016年，戴维加入了渥太华国际。<ref name="CSA" />

==俱乐部生涯==
===根特===
2018年1月，戴维加盟了[[比利时足球甲级联赛|比甲]]球队[[皇家根特体育会|根特]]。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2018-01-23 |title=OISC Youth Player Signs First Pro Contact |url=http://www.ottawasoccer.com/Default.asp?id=clubinfo-announcements&l=1&a=article&cid=565 |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711100658/http://www.ottawasoccer.com/Default.asp?id=clubinfo-announcements&l=1&a=article&cid=565 }}</ref>同年8月4日，在根特与1-1战平[[瓦勒海姆聚尔特体育俱乐部|瓦勒海姆聚尔特体育]]的比赛中，戴维完成了一线队首秀，并在伤停补时打进了扳平一球，帮助球队拿到一分。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Nuyens |first=Rudy |date=2018-08-04 |title=Gent voorkomt nul op zes in slotseconden: nieuwkomer David scoort late gelijkmaker tegen Zulte Waregem |url=https://m.hln.be/sport/voetbal/belgisch-voetbal/jupiler-pro-league/gent-voorkomt-nul-op-zes-in-slotseconden-nieuwkomer-david-scoort-late-gelijkmaker-tegen-zulte-waregem~a2898be7/ |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2018-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805113951/https://m.hln.be/sport/voetbal/belgisch-voetbal/jupiler-pro-league/gent-voorkomt-nul-op-zes-in-slotseconden-nieuwkomer-david-scoort-late-gelijkmaker-tegen-zulte-waregem~a2898be7/ }}</ref>在他上演联赛首秀的5天后，戴维在根特1-0战胜[[乔治罗尼亚比亚韦斯托克足球俱乐部|乔治罗尼亚比亚韦斯托克]]的[[欧联杯|欧联杯]][[2018–19年欧洲联赛预选赛及附加赛轮_(主要途径)|第三轮预选赛]]的下半场中替补登场，并在第85分钟打入了制胜一球，帮助球队进军欧联杯正赛。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2018-08-08 |title=UEFA Europa League - Jagiellonia Białystok-Gent |url=https://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2019/matches/round=2000988/match=2025347/index.html |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2019-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217080200/https://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2019/matches/round=2000988/match=2025347/index.html }}</ref>3天后，戴维再次打进了进球，在根特4-1大胜[[华斯兰德贝弗伦|华斯兰德贝弗伦]]的联赛的第71分钟替补登场，并打进了两粒进球。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2018-08-12 |title=JUPILER PRO LEAGUE – MATCHDAY 3 |url=https://www.kaagent.be/en/team/games/jupiler-pro-league-2018-2019/3/kaa-gent/waasland-beveren/digest |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2018-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180813043257/https://www.kaagent.be/en/team/games/jupiler-pro-league-2018-2019/3/kaa-gent/waasland-beveren/digest }}</ref>在为一线队出战的前5场比赛中打进了5粒进球后，根特与戴维续约至了2022年。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2018-08-20 |title=La Gantoise sécurise son talent Jonathan David en le prolongeant jusqu’en 2022 |url=https://www.lavenir.net/cnt/dmf20180820_01211520/la-gantoise-securise-son-talent-jonathan-david-en-le-prolongeant-jusqu-en-2022 |website=Lavenir |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026132213/https://www.lavenir.net/cnt/dmf20180820_01211520/la-gantoise-securise-son-talent-jonathan-david-en-le-prolongeant-jusqu-en-2022 }}</ref>2019年9月，戴维再次与俱乐部续约一年，新的合同直到2023年才会到期。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2019-09-24 |title=AA Gent legt goudhaantje Jonathan David langer vast |url=https://m.nieuwsblad.be/cnt/dmf20190923_04623310 |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2021-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210425071200/https://m.nieuwsblad.be/cnt/dmf20190923_04623310 }}</ref>在2020年1月的冬季转会窗时，根特主席伊万·德维特表示，戴维受到了多家大俱乐部的关注，若他最终被根特出售，转会费将会达到至少2000万欧元。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2020-01-08 |title=Jonathan David Niet te Koop Voor 20 Miljoen Euro |url=https://www.voetbalbelgie.be/specials/jonathan-david-niet-te-koop-voor-20-miljoen-euro/2020/01/08/ |website=Voetbal Belgie |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2020-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200111152953/https://www.voetbalbelgie.be/specials/jonathan-david-niet-te-koop-voor-20-miljoen-euro/2020/01/08/ }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2020-01-07 |title=Jonathan David: "Ik zal altijd voor mijn moeder spelen" |url=https://sporza.be/nl/2020/01/06/jonathan-david-stage/ |website=Sporza |language=nl |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122203005/https://sporza.be/nl/2020/01/06/jonathan-david-stage/ }}</ref>

===里尔===
2020年8月11日，[[法国足球甲级联赛|法甲]]球队[[里尔足球俱乐部|里尔]]官方宣布，俱乐部已经签下了戴维，合同为期5年，将会在2025年到期。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2020-08-11 |title=Jonathan David au LOSC, c’est fait ! |url=https://www.losc.fr/actualites-foot-lille/%E2%80%8Bjonathan-david-au-losc-c’est-fait |access-date=2020-08-11 |publisher=[[里尔足球俱乐部|里尔]]官网 |language=fr |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124003342/https://www.losc.fr/actualites-foot-lille/%E2%80%8Bjonathan-david-au-losc-c%E2%80%99est-fait }}</ref>据媒体报道，戴维的转会费约为3000万欧元，他也就此成为了转会费最高昂的加拿大足球运动员。<ref>{{Cite news |last=Rouse |first=Daniel |date=2020-08-11 |title=Lille make Jonathan David most expensive Canadian player ever |work=theScore |url=https://www.thescore.com/s/14907314 |access-date=2020-08-11}}</ref>同年8月22日，在里尔1-1战平[[雷恩足球俱乐部|雷恩]]的[[2020年至2021年法国足球甲级联赛|法甲]]赛季首战中，戴维完成了里尔首秀。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Quillan |first=Ian |date=2020-08-22 |title=Canada's Jonathan David starts in Ligue 1 debut as Lille hold on for draw against Stade Rennes |url=https://www.mlssoccer.com/post/2020/08/22/canadas-jonathan-david-starts-ligue-1-debut-lille-hold-draw-against-stade-rennes |access-date=2021-03-28 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030045915/https://www.mlssoccer.com/post/2020/08/22/canadas-jonathan-david-starts-ligue-1-debut-lille-hold-draw-against-stade-rennes }}</ref>在经历了一个困难的开始后，戴维在11月22日里尔4-0完胜[[洛里昂足球俱乐部|洛里昂]]的比赛中打进了球队的最后一粒进球，这同样也是他为里尔打进的第一粒进球。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tsn.ca/canadian-jonathan-david-scores-first-goal-in-lille-win-1.1555186|title=Canada's David scores first goal in Lille win|date=2020-11-22|access-date=2021-03-28|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129091749/https://www.tsn.ca/canadian-jonathan-david-scores-first-goal-in-lille-win-1.1555186}}</ref>在连续7场比赛没有取得进球后，<ref>{{cite web |title=Canadian Jonathan David nets winner, Lille beats Reims |url=https://www.tsn.ca/canada-forward-david-nets-late-winner-as-lille-beats-reims-1.1578668 |website=tsn.ca |access-date=2021-02-03 |date=2020-01-17 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204102234/https://www.tsn.ca/canada-forward-david-nets-late-winner-as-lille-beats-reims-1.1578668 }}</ref>戴维在1月17日里尔2-1险胜[[兰斯体育俱乐部|兰斯]]的联赛中一击制胜，绝杀对手，并帮助球队超过[[巴黎圣日耳曼足球俱乐部|巴黎圣日耳曼]]的积分，登顶积分榜榜首。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Pugmire |first1=Jerome |title=David scores as Lille wins 1-0 to stay level with leader PSG |url=https://apnews.com/article/lille-romain-salin-jonathan-david-ligue-1-nayef-aguerd-452d6ea0ed42b69f5fe970dc88da2c02 |access-date=2021-02-03 |work=AP新闻 |date=2021-01-24 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208001719/https://apnews.com/article/lille-romain-salin-jonathan-david-ligue-1-nayef-aguerd-452d6ea0ed42b69f5fe970dc88da2c02 }}</ref>2021年2月3日，戴维在里尔3-0客胜[[波尔多足球俱乐部|波尔多]]的联赛中再次打进了一粒进球。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Pugmire |first1=Jerome |title=Weah, David score for leader Lille in 3-0 win at Bordeaux |url=https://apnews.com/article/lyon-lille-yusuf-yazici-george-weah-jonathan-bamba-490f76c24cfe57ff74652c00c94f61bc |access-date=2021-02-03 |work=AP新闻 |date=2021-02-03 |archive-date=2021-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209035901/https://apnews.com/article/lyon-lille-yusuf-yazici-george-weah-jonathan-bamba-490f76c24cfe57ff74652c00c94f61bc }}</ref>2月7日，在里尔2-0战胜[[南特足球俱乐部|南特]]的联赛中，戴维继续延伸着他火热的状态，在加盟里尔以来首次连场进球，包揽了该场比赛中的全部两粒进球。在赛季前半程仅仅打进两粒进球后，戴维在连场进球后（不包括之后的比赛）已经打进了5粒进球，合计7球。2021年4月3日，戴维在里尔1-0客胜[[巴黎圣日耳曼足球俱乐部|巴黎圣日耳曼]]的法甲比赛中打进了制胜一球，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/report?gameId=572965 |title=Neymar sees red as Lille move top with win over Paris Saint-Germain |website=ESPN |date=2021-04-03 |access-date=2021-04-05 |archive-date=2021-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404000449/https://www.espn.com/soccer/report?gameId=572965 }}</ref>帮助俱乐部自1996年4月以来首次在[[王子公园球场|王子公园球场]]击败巴黎圣日耳曼。<ref>{{cite tweet |user=OptaJean |title=Paris n’a perdu aucune de ses 21 dernières réceptions de Lille en Ligue 1 (13 victoires, 8 nuls), son dernier revers à domicile face au LOSC en championnat remontant au 27 avril 1996 (0-1) |number=1378308449713451012 |language=fr |date=2021-04-03 }}</ref>但是在比赛中，戴维被巴黎球员铲伤，将会缺席球队之后的数场比赛。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.zhibo8.cc/zuqiu/2021-04-06/606b4438587e9.htm|title=官方：在对巴黎比赛中被铲伤右脚踝韧带，里尔前锋戴维将缺阵数周|author=直播吧|date=2021-04-05}}</ref>

==国家队生涯==
===国青队===
2015年，在参加了几个加拿大U-15的训练营后，戴维首次被加拿大青年国家队发现，并在{{le|2017年中北美洲及加勒比海足协U-17冠军赛|2017 CONCACAF U-17 Championship|2017年U-17CONCACAF冠军赛}}开始前被{{le|加拿大17岁以下国家足球队|Canada men's national under-17 soccer team|加拿大U-17}}国家队征召进入了球队的赛前备战大名单中。<ref name="CSA" />戴维入选了最终的U-17大名单中，<ref>{{Cite web |date=2017-04-11 |title=Canada announces squad for CONCACAF Men's Under-17 Championship |url=https://www.canadasoccer.com/canada-announces-squad-for-concacaf-men-s-under-17-championship-p160714 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170420033449/https://www.canadasoccer.com/canada-announces-squad-for-concacaf-men-s-under-17-championship-p160714 |archive-date=2017-04-20 |website=canadasoccer.com}}</ref>并在加拿大U-17与[[苏里南国家足球队|苏里南]]U-17的小组赛第三场中梅开二度。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Rosano |first=Nick |date=2017-04-28 |title=Canada bow out of CONCACAF U-17 Championship with 2–0 win vs. Suriname |url=https://www.mlssoccer.com/post/2017/04/28/canada-bow-out-concacaf-u-17-championship-2-0-win-vs-suriname |access-date=2021-03-28 |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812160554/https://www.mlssoccer.com/post/2017/04/28/canada-bow-out-concacaf-u-17-championship-2-0-win-vs-suriname }}</ref>2018年5月，戴维入选了{{le|加拿大23岁以下国家足球队|Canada men's national under-23 soccer team|加拿大U-23}}的[[土伦杯|土伦杯]]大名单。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Tierney |first=Mitchell |date=2018-05-17 |title=Canada’s next generation will be on display at the Toulon Tournament |url=https://www.wakingthered.com/2018/5/17/17366008/canadas-roster-toulon-tournament-2018-france-liam-millar |access-date=2021-03-28 |archive-date=2018-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180707100611/https://www.wakingthered.com/2018/5/17/17366008/canadas-roster-toulon-tournament-2018-france-liam-millar }}</ref>

戴维曾被{{le|美国20岁以下国家足球队|United States men's national under-20 soccer team|美国U-20}}国家队主帅{{le|塔博·拉莫斯|Tab Ramos|拉莫斯}}征召，但他婉拒了对方的邀请，因为他更想专注于自己的俱乐部，并且只想为加拿大出战。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Cardenas |first=Felipe |title=‘What has happened to me is really unbelievable’:... |url=https://theathletic.com/1052823/2019/06/28/what-has-happened-to-me-is-really-unbelievable-jonathan-davids-rise-from-amateur-soccer-to-canadas-national-team/ |access-date=2019-11-26 |website=The Athletic |archive-date=2021-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210613075745/https://theathletic.com/1052823/2019/06/28/what-has-happened-to-me-is-really-unbelievable-jonathan-davids-rise-from-amateur-soccer-to-canadas-national-team/ }}</ref>

===国家队===
2018年8月30日，戴维首次收到了[[加拿大国家足球队|-{加拿大国家队}-]]的征召，将会参加加拿大与[[美属维尔京群岛足球代表队|美属维尔京群岛]]的[[2019–20年中北美洲及加勒比海国家联赛外围赛|2019–20赛季CONCACAF国家联赛预选赛]]。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2018-08-30 |title=Canada Soccer announces squad for Concacaf Nations League Qualifying |url=https://www.canadasoccer.com/canada-soccer-announces-squad-for-concacaf-nations-league-qualifying-p161777-preview-1 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180830174512/https://www.canadasoccer.com/canada-soccer-announces-squad-for-concacaf-nations-league-qualifying-p161777-preview-1 |archive-date=2018-08-30 |website=canadasoccer.com}}</ref>9月9日，他在比赛中登场，完成了大国家队首秀，并在比赛中梅开二度，帮助加拿大8-0血洗对手。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2018-09-09 |title=Canada cruises to record win in Concacaf Nations League opener |url=https://www.sportsnet.ca/soccer/canada-cruises-record-victory-u-s-virgin-islands/ |access-date=2021-03-28 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109032749/https://www.sportsnet.ca/soccer/canada-cruises-record-victory-u-s-virgin-islands/ }}</ref>2019年5月30日，戴维入选了加拿大征战[[2019年美洲金盃|2019年中北美金杯]]的最终大名单中。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2019-05-30 |title=Together We Rise: Canada Soccer announces squad for the 2019 Concacaf Gold Cup |url=https://www.canadasoccer.com/together-we-rise-canada-soccer-announces-squad-for-the-2019-concacaf-gold-cup-p162198 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603025211/https://www.canadasoccer.com/together-we-rise-canada-soccer-announces-squad-for-the-2019-concacaf-gold-cup-p162198 |archive-date=2020-07-03 |website=canadasoccer.com}}</ref>在加拿大7-0完胜[[古巴国家足球队|古巴]]的小组赛第三场中，戴维上演了帽子戏法。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2019-06-23 |title=Cavallini, David hat tricks lead Canada past Cuba in Gold Cup |url=https://www.tsn.ca/lucas-cavallini-jonathan-david-hat-tricks-lead-canada-past-cuba-in-gold-cup-1.1327481 |publisher=The Sports Network |access-date=2021-03-28 |archive-date=2019-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190624185037/https://www.tsn.ca/lucas-cavallini-jonathan-david-hat-tricks-lead-canada-past-cuba-in-gold-cup-1.1327481 }}</ref>在加拿大与[[海地国家足球队|海地]]的1/4决赛中，戴维打进了一粒进球，但没能挽回败局，最终加拿大2-3惜败，被对手淘汰出局。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Heroux |first=Devin |date=2019-06-29 |title=Canada crashes out of Gold Cup quarters after coughing up lead to Haiti |url=https://www.cbc.ca/sports/soccer/gold-cup-canada-haiti-quarter-finals-1.5195605 |access-date=2021-03-28 |archive-date=2021-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117083754/https://www.cbc.ca/sports/soccer/gold-cup-canada-haiti-quarter-finals-1.5195605 }}</ref>赛事结束后，戴维合计打进了6球，获得了赛事金靴奖。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2019-07-08 |title=2019 Concacaf Gold Cup – Golden Boot Award |url=https://www.goldcup.org/en/awards/golden-boot-award |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2019-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190708072406/https://www.goldcup.org/en/awards/golden-boot-award }}</ref>

2019年9月7日，在加拿大6-0大胜[[古巴国家足球队|古巴]]的比赛中，在进球后，戴维已经在2019年合计打进了8球，从而创造了加拿大球员在一个自然年内为大国家队中打进最多进球的记录。<ref>{{Cite news |title=Canada lights up Cuba, earns clean sheet to kick off Nations League campaign |agency=The Canadian Press |url=https://www.cbc.ca/sports/soccer/nations-league-canada-cuba-first-leg-1.5275029 |access-date=2019-09-08 |archive-date=2019-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191026081923/https://www.cbc.ca/sports/soccer/nations-league-canada-cuba-first-leg-1.5275029 }}</ref>为了表彰他的贡献，戴维被评为{{le|加拿大年度最佳足球运动员|Canadian Players of the Year|2019年加拿大年度最佳男子足球运动员}}。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2019-12-11 |title=Canada Soccer announces Jonathan David as 2019 Canadian Player of the Year |url=https://www.canadasoccer.com/canada-soccer-announces-jonathan-david-as-2019-canadian-player-of-the-year-p162517 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213082212/https://www.canadasoccer.com/canada-soccer-announces-jonathan-david-as-2019-canadian-player-of-the-year-p162517 |archive-date=2019-12-13 |website=canadasoccer.com}}</ref>

==个人生活==
戴维于2000年1月14日出生在[[美国|美国]][[纽约州|纽约州]][[纽约市|纽约市]]的[[布鲁克林|布鲁克林]]行政区，他的父母均为海地人。在他三个月大的时候，他来到了[[海地|海地]][[太子港|太子港]]居住。<ref name="CSA" /><ref name="RCI" />6岁时，他与他的父母移民至[[加拿大|加拿大]]，并在[[渥太华|渥太华]]定居。<ref name="CSA" />他曾在法语学校{{link-fr|路易·瑞耶尔公立中学|École secondaire publique Louis-Riel}}接受教育。戴维曾在接受采访时表示：“在路易·瑞耶尔中学读书的时候，我提升了我的控球技术，这也是我成功的原因之一”。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Jonathan David, la nouvelle coqueluche du soccer Canadien |url=https://www.ici.radio-canada.ca/amp/1122870/jonathan-david-gent-nouvelle-coqueluche-football-soccer-canadien- |access-date=2019-06-18 |publisher=CBC/Radio-Canada |archive-date=2021-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523231909/https://ici.radio-canada.ca/amp/1122870/jonathan-david-gent-nouvelle-coqueluche-football-soccer-canadien- }}</ref>

在戴维成长的过程中，他从来没有观看过{{le|加拿大的足球|soccer in Canada|加拿大联赛}}或[[美国职业足球大联盟|美职联]]的比赛。他从来没有过任何为北美洲的球队登场比赛的想法，但他非常渴望为欧洲球队出战。<ref name="Eliasy">{{Cite news |last=Eliasy |first=Alain |date=2019-10-29 |title=Jonathan David, goudhaantje van KAA Gent: 'Tijdens mijn puberteit had ik even andere prioriteiten' |work=Sport Voetbal Magazine |url=https://sportmagazine.knack.be/sport/voetbal-internationaal/jonathan-david-goudhaantje-van-kaa-gent-tijdens-mijn-puberteit-had-ik-even-andere-prioriteiten/article-normal-1525807.html?cookie_check=1572411621#Echobox=1572347734 |accessdate=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2021-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527032209/https://sportmagazine.knack.be/sport/voetbal-internationaal/jonathan-david-goudhaantje-van-kaa-gent-tijdens-mijn-puberteit-had-ik-even-andere-prioriteiten/article-normal-1525807.html?cookie_check=1572411621#Echobox=1572347734 }}</ref>

